"{\"uid\": \"sheknows.com-entertainment-articles-3074752-tom-cruise-nicole-kidman-olympics-paris-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"byAlice Kelly  Tom CruiseandNicole Kidmanare both in Paris for the 2024Olympicsbut managed to avoid seeing each other.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 118, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8, \"end\": 13, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Osbourne\", \"score\": 0.9999999987851425, \"rank\": 1.1866166625483331e-09, \"text\": \"Kelly\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Osbourne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Osbourne\"}, {\"begin\": 53, \"end\": 58, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999995828412427, \"rank\": 4.17159013912022e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The two actors are among many otherA-listers who are in the French capitalfor this year's Games, joining stars like Ariana Grande, Spike Lee and Nick Jonas in the stands.\", \"from\": 120, \"to\": 290, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 236, \"end\": 249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariana_Grande\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ariana Grande\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariana_Grande\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariana_Grande\"}, {\"begin\": 251, \"end\": 256, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paramount_Network\", \"score\": 0.9999998034729936, \"rank\": 1.9652697716586193e-07, \"text\": \"Spike\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paramount_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paramount_Network\"}, {\"begin\": 257, \"end\": 260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Not_Going_Out\", \"score\": 0.9990054422872258, \"rank\": 0.00097943553689678, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Not_Going_Out\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Not_Going_Out\"}, {\"begin\": 265, \"end\": 275, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Jonas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5059939314028572e-30, \"text\": \"Nick Jonas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Jonas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Jonas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But with so many incredible athletes battling it out for medals in so many different sports, the exes had no problem avoiding each other.\", \"from\": 291, \"to\": 428, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On July 28, Cruisewatched Simone Bilesat her high-anticipated Olympics redemption during the women's artistic gymnastics qualification round.Related storyTyra Banks Looks Unrecognizable With Her Shortest & Most Old Hollywood Inspired Hairdo to Date  Kidman, who was married to Cruise from 1990 until 2001, managed to miss a run-in with her ex when she  watched the Artistic Gymnastics Women's Team Final on July 30, just two days after Cruise was in the same arena.\", \"from\": 430, \"to\": 895, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 804, \"end\": 814, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artistic_gymnastics\", \"score\": 0.9720277365070383, \"rank\": 0.02858552323878683, \"text\": \"Gymnastics\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artistic_gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artistic_gymnastics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Oscar-winner joined husband Keith Urban and their two daughters, Sunday Rose, 16, and Faith, 13, to watch Biles lead Team USA Gymnastics to gold.\", \"from\": 897, \"to\": 1046, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 929, \"end\": 940, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keith_Urban\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.118994671261699e-31, \"text\": \"Keith Urban\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keith_Urban\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keith_Urban\"}, {\"begin\": 1023, \"end\": 1037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\", \"score\": 0.9999946003665889, \"rank\": 5.399662480001949e-06, \"text\": \"USA Gymnastics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kidman also shared the arena with four-time Olympic medalist, Serena Williams, and fellow actress Natalie Portman.\", \"from\": 1048, \"to\": 1162, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1110, \"end\": 1125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serena_Williams\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Serena Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serena_Williams\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serena_Williams\"}, {\"begin\": 1146, \"end\": 1161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Natalie_Portman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Natalie Portman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Natalie_Portman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Natalie_Portman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kidman and Cruise do not make a habit out of appearing at the same events ever since their high-profile split - it was even reported last year that theMission: Impossiblestar deliberatelyskipped the 2023 Oscarsto avoid his ex-wife.\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1395, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Kidman did givea rare comment about Cruisein an interview early in July.\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1477, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While discussing her and Cruise's hit 1999 psychological drama,Eyes Wide Shut,Kidman revealed that director Stanley Kubrick pried into the couple's relationship while they were working on the movie.\", \"from\": 1479, \"to\": 1677, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1587, \"end\": 1602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stanley_Kubrick\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stanley Kubrick\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stanley_Kubrick\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stanley_Kubrick\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I suppose he was mining [our marriage],\\\" the star said to theLos Angeles Times.\", \"from\": 1679, \"to\": 1759, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There were ideas he was interested in.\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1799, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He'd ask a lot of questions.\\\"\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1829, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kidman said she never felt ganged up on by the director but admitted that Cruise might have had a different experience on set.\", \"from\": 1830, \"to\": 1956, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is something about being a woman in that equation, too,\\\" Kidman reflected.\", \"from\": 1958, \"to\": 2039, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He had a different relationship with Tom.\", \"from\": 2040, \"to\": 2082, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They worked more closely together on his character.\\\"\", \"from\": 2083, \"to\": 2135, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Before you go, click to seeathlete power couples who both competed at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2137, \"to\": 2220, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The stories you care about, delivered daily.\", \"from\": 2222, \"to\": 2266, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SheKnows is a part of Penske Media Corporation.\", \"from\": 2268, \"to\": 2315, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2268, \"end\": 2276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SHE_Media\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"SheKnows\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resou